    "Key features such as modeling, visualization, and programming foster mathematical experiments and discoveries (Ziatdinov & Valles, 2022).",
    "Studies have shown GeoGebra's effectiveness in enhancing students' understanding of geometric concepts, including transformations and circle theorems (Bhagat & Chang, 2015; Dahal et al., 2019; Bayaga et al., 2019).",
    "The software enables students to construct, manipulate, and visualize geometric shapes, thereby making abstract concepts more tangible (Boo, 2016; Velichová, 2011).",
    "The second cluster, \"GeoGebra in Mathematics Teaching,\" focuses on investigating the impact of GeoGebra on mathematics teaching, particularly in areas such as technology integration, teacher training, and the design of innovative learning environments.",
